SELECT HUNTS.HUNT_ID,to_char(HUNTS.hunt_date, 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS HUNT_DATE,HUNTS.ANIMALS_HUNTED/(HUNTS.DURATION*HUNTS.NUMBER_OF_PEOPLE)AS HUNT_FACTOR,HUNTS.NUMBER_OF_PEOPLE,MEMBERS.MEMBER_ID,ANIMALS.ANIMAL_ID,roles.role_id,outcome.outcome_id FROM HUNTS INNER JOIN MEMBERS ON members.hunt_id=hunts.hunt_id INNER JOIN ANIMALS ON animals.hunt_id=hunts.hunt_id INNER JOIN hunt_meeting_participants ON hunt_meeting_participants.member_id=members.member_id INNER JOIN ROLES ON roles.role_id=hunt_meeting_participants.role_id INNER JOIN hunt_meetings ON hunt_meetings.hunt_id=hunts.hunt_id INNER JOIN OUTCOME ON outcome.outcome_id=hunt_meetings.hunt_meeting_id

SELECT ANIMALS.ANIMAL_ID, to_char(CATCHES.CATCH_DATE, 'yyyy-mm-dd') AS CATCH_DATE, ANIMALS.WEIGHT_KG * SPECIES.PRICE_PER_KG * (SPECIES.POPULATION_STATUS/10000 + 0.5) AS TOTAL_PRICE, 10 - (5 - ANIMALS.HEALTH_STATUS/2) - (ANIMALS.AGE/(2*10)) AS MEAT_QUALITY, CATCHES.CATCH_ID, SPECIES.SPECIE_ID, HUNTS.HUNT_ID, HUNTERS.HUNTER_ID, LOCATIONS.LOCATION_ID FROM ANIMALS INNER JOIN CATCHES ON CATCHES.CATCH_ID = ANIMALS.CATCH_ID INNER JOIN SPECIES ON SPECIES.SPECIE_ID = ANIMALS.SPECIE_ID INNER JOIN HUNTS ON HUNTS.HUNT_ID = CATCHES.HUNT_ID INNER JOIN HUNTERS ON HUNTERS.HUNTER_ID = CATCHES.HUNTER_ID INNER JOIN LOCATIONS ON LOCATIONS.LOCATION_ID = HUNTS.LOCATION_ID
